.SH NAME
.PP
rg \- recursively search current directory for lines matching a pattern
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
rg [\f[I]options\f[]] \-e PATTERN ...
[\f[I]<\f[]path\f[I]> ...\f[]]
.PP
rg [\f[I]options\f[]] <\f[I]pattern\f[]> [\f[I]<\f[]path\f[I]> ...\f[]]
.PP
rg [\f[I]options\f[]] \-\-files [\f[I]<\f[]path\f[I]> ...\f[]]
.PP
