.PP
rg [\f[I]options\f[]] \-\-help
.PP
rg [\f[I]options\f[]] \-\-version
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
rg (ripgrep) combines the usability of The Silver Searcher (an ack
clone) with the raw speed of grep.
